      "HICAGO, ILLINOTS\nUnited Air Lines\nUnited's\nBig\nNew One\nCLOSE COVER BEFORE STRIKING MATCH",
      "United's Big New Ome..",
      "Only United flies\nthe Super DC-8 to Hawaii\nAnd we're making the most of it!\nBright decor, colorful costumes,\nauthentic Hawaiian food and bever-\nages make our Super DC-8 flights\none big luau all the way!",
